high_descs: Turn around and go near the side table.
Take the soap bar from the side table.
Turn around and go near the floor lamp.
Put the soap bar near the floor lamp and it will be glow.
anns.task_desc: Placed the soap bar near the floor lamp and it will be glow.

high_descs: Turn around to the nightstand next to the bed.
Pick up the bar of soap from the nightstand.
Turn around and approach the lamp in the corner of the room ahead.
anns.task_desc: Hold up a bar of soap to a lit lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the side table.
Pick up soap bar from the side table.
Turn around and turn left and then head straight towards the floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a soap bar by the light of a floor lamp.
